{
  "text": "The collected sera were used for determination of the activity of both (AST) aspirate aminotransferase and (ALT) alanine aminotransferase as liver markers. In addition, levels of blood urea, serum creatinine were also estimated as kidney markers [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
